data.news_body:
This is to inform you that the Board of Directors of the Company at their Meeting held today i.e. Wednesday January 28 2026 has inter-alia considered and approved the
1. Unaudited Financial Results (Standalone and Consolidated) of the Company for the third quarter and nine months ended December 31 2025;
2. Interim Dividend of Rs. 8.00 /- (Rupees Eight only) per equity share of face value of Rs. 2/- (Rupees Two only) each fully paid up for the Financial Year 2025-26;
3. Approved the Postal Ballot Notice .
